Package org.apache.axis2.transport.testkit.filter Description

Provides classes to evaluate LDAP filters against Map objects.

LDAP filter expressions are parsed using FilterExpressionParser.parse(String). The resulting FilterExpression object can then be used to evaluate the filter against a given Map object.

See Also:
RFC2254: The String Representation of LDAP Search Filters
